txt.en: Dagor can be found in Arnach, near the keep.\n\nYou should return to Dagor and tell him of the blow you have struck to the foe.
'Ha ha! My plan goes well apace. Thank you, [placeholder]. We will soon send these Southrons back with their tails between their legs!'
'Ha ha! My plan goes well apace. Thank you, [placeholder]. We will soon send these Southrons back with their tails between their legs!'

'We may not be the lucky few, gone to fight at Minas Tirith. But we may still use martial tactics and strategies! The Southron foe despoils Lossarnach soil, and I have a plan to deal them a decisive blow.

'A bundle of sticks is strong, whilst any one twig may be broken. We must seek out the Harad swordsmen in their camps and hideaways, and strike them before they strike at us in force! 

'Duty binds me to my post, here. But you, [placeholder], could help to strike this blow and win the glory in so doing!'
Dagor has a daring plan to diminish the attacking power of the Haradrim invaders.
Dagor: A Strike at the Hands
Haradrim invaders can be found east and south of Arnach.\n\nYou should defeat a number of Haradrim Devoted while they are scattered, so there are fewer to attack in force.
